manifest.jsonl
tasks/_status_snapshot.json
tasks/_tick_status.json

# cpu pilot: text EVIDENCE is committable (manifest, tokenizer json, per-step metrics jsonl);
# checkpoints/shards are NOT (*.pt/*.bin above keep binaries out regardless). Rationale: a fresh
# clone can then verify the manifest against its metrics/tokenizer without rerunning the 15-min
# chain, while idx sidecars (regenerable with the shards) stay ignored — their tests skip-if-absent.
!runs/
runs/*
!runs/cpu_pilot/
runs/cpu_pilot/*
!runs/cpu_pilot/MANIFEST.json
!runs/cpu_pilot/tokenizer/
!runs/cpu_pilot/reports/
!runs/cpu_pilot/reports/**
